item.content:
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data/uploads/pic.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-8&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;An Innovative procedure to treat Common bile duct stone and Gall bladder stone done at &lt;strong&gt;Gateway clinics&lt;/strong&gt; by a team of doctors led by &lt;strong&gt;Dr. K. Sendhil Kumar&lt;/strong&gt; and Team Members Dr. Piyush Patwa &amp;amp; Dr. K. Karthik which grabbed Best Innovation paper award in Indian National Surgeon&#039;s conference ASICON 2019 proves itself at international platform. The paper is accepted in SAGES 2020 Annual meeting- Vision 2020: Rockin&#039; the future with Innovation and Discovery. The Society of American Gastrointestinal and Endoscopic Surgeons will showcase this Innovative technique and achievement during its national annual congress to be held in August 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Abstract Title :&amp;nbsp;Laparoscopy guided transcystic Cholangioscopic holmium laser lithotripsy of a large impacted common bile duct stone after failed ERCP&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
